NATIONAL MILK PRODUCERS FEDERATION, aka Cooperatives Working Together, et al., petitioners,
v.
Matthew EDWARDS, Individually and on Behalf of All Others Similarly Situated, et al. No. 14-1078. Supreme Court of the United States April 27, 2015.

Opinion

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
